00:00:13.288 --> 00:00:20.176
Hi! Welcome to Aha Emi Ruchi!

00:00:37.152 --> 00:00:44.458
What will you be cooking for us?
Tomato Stew (Pulusu)

00:00:49.151 --> 00:00:51.516
Ingredients required to make Tomato Stew

00:00:51.961 --> 00:01:04.666
Tomatoes, Green Chillies, Coriander, Curry Leaves, Onions,
 Turmeric, Salt, Red Chilli Powder, Ginger Garlic Paste, Oil

00:01:30.366 --> 00:01:39.297
Take a pan and heat some oil

00:01:53.063 --> 00:02:04.357
Add some mustard seeds, cumin, garlic, dry red chilli, bengal gram, white lentils

00:02:23.370 --> 00:02:29.597
Add a few curry leaves

00:02:41.002 --> 00:02:47.530
Add a few big green chillies

00:02:59.283 --> 00:03:06.872
Add some chopped onions

00:03:31.191 --> 00:03:44.776
Cut the unripe tomatoes in big pieces and add them

00:04:12.640 --> 00:04:19.384
Add a little salt for taste

00:04:32.140 --> 00:04:37.482
Add a pinch of turmeric

00:04:45.317 --> 00:04:49.815
Add some ginger, garlic and green chilli paste

00:05:08.764 --> 00:05:16.965
Add 1/2 tbsp of red chilli powder

00:05:26.454 --> 00:05:38.094
So, instead of tamarind juice we'll be using tomato puree/paste

00:05:44.907 --> 00:05:52.826
Add some tomato puree

00:05:55.581 --> 00:06:02.866
Add a little water

00:06:11.595 --> 00:06:17.116
Serve it in a bowl

00:06:19.659 --> 00:06:21.247
Garnish with some coriander

